          "description": "While the individual dentists and technicians at this practice are all very nice, this is unfortunately another sketchy nyc dentist to avoid. I had a scheduled cavity filling and ended up waiting for more than an hour to be seen, having to remind them more than once that I was still waiting. The fillings were incredibly expensive, and I\u2019ve had a lot of pain since that filling, which has never happened before. The ongoing process of trying to schedule another appointment with their horrible AI \u201cassistant\u201d that answers all the phones has been so slow and frustrating that I\u2019ll probably need to schedule with another dentist for corrections. Take your insurance, money, and precious teeth elsewhere.",
